      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pretty-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ある日の打ち合わせにて",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "えー！？　芽衣がもし恋のヒロインに選ばれたの！？\n怜ちゃんと渚ちゃんが出てたやつだよね！？",
      "startTime": 6.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。夏休み前の忙しいところ申し訳ないが\nぜひ芽衣に協力してほしいとのことだ",
      "startTime": 14.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "楽しそう！　芽衣にやらせて！\nあのゲームのヒロインになれるなんて嬉しいな～",
      "startTime": 20.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣も怜ちゃんみたいに、最初は冷たいけど\n実は優しい子っていう設定だったりして",
      "startTime": 28.8999988556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "渚ちゃんみたいな、幼なじみっていう設定もいいよね\n朝から家に「おはよー」って起こしに行くの！",
      "startTime": 37.2999988556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "ねえねえ、{user}さん！\n芽衣のお話はどんな感じになるの？",
      "startTime": 43.2999988556,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6610.001144399995,
          "startTime": 49.91
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そのことなんだが\nまずはこの書類に目を通してほしいんだ",
      "startTime": 48.4666655223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "えっと、これはアンケート？\n恋愛観に、好きなシチュエーション……",
      "startTime": 57.2333321889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "理想のデートに、告白について……\nこれに書いたことが、そのままゲームになるの？",
      "startTime": 68.1999988556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "さすがに全部とまではいかないだろうが\n芽衣の意向をなるべく尊重したいと先方は言っていたな",
      "startTime": 75.0666655223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんだ！　よーっし、頑張って埋めちゃうよ！\nでも、恋愛観って何を書けばいいんだろう？",
      "startTime": 84.6666655223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "こういう恋愛がしてみたい、とか\n芽衣が思う理想の恋愛について書いてくれればいいぞ",
      "startTime": 92.7999988556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "理想の恋愛か～\nうーん……何かあるかなぁ……",
      "startTime": 100.0666655223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "む、難しいなぁ……むむむむ……\nこれ、寮に持って帰って、もう少し考えてみてもいい？",
      "startTime": 112.9999988556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "急ぎじゃないから、それでも構わないよ\nじっくり考えてきてくれ",
      "startTime": 120.9333321889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "startTime": 124.1922056119,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "アンケート全部埋めてきたよ～！　理想の恋愛とか\n理想のデートとか、しっかり書いてきたよ！",
      "startTime": 130.2000059764,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5329.994023599994,
          "startTime": 135.53
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう。どれどれ……ん？\n「お菓子のお家を一緒に作る」……？",
      "startTime": 138.1333393097,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "凄く楽しそうでしょ？　好きな人と一緒に\n二人の大好きなお菓子を使ってお家を作るの！",
      "startTime": 146.2333393097,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣はドーナツで作る、と。確かに楽しそうだが……\nこれが……芽衣の考える理想の恋愛……か？",
      "startTime": 156.566672643,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-mei013.m4a",
      "text": "うん！　『理想の恋愛』って、どういうことかなーって\n芽衣なりに、いーっぱい考えてみたんだ",
      "startTime": 166.7333393097,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-mei014.m4a",
      "text": "好きな人と、楽しいことを一緒にするって恋愛っぽい\nでしょ？　それにゲームだし、夢があったらいいなって",
      "startTime": 174.7736046612,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "な、なるほど……\nこの「猫ちゃんの集会に参加する」というのは？",
      "startTime": 181.466672643,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-mei015.m4a",
      "text": "夜の公園で、猫ちゃん達がよく集まってるでしょ？\nそこに二人で参加するの！",
      "startTime": 189.8304944113,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-mei016.m4a",
      "text": "近所の公園でも、たまに集まってるのをみるんだ～\nそうだ！　猫ちゃんの言葉が話せたらもっと楽しいよね",
      "startTime": 196.4894612473,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "ゲームはゲームでも、今回は恋愛ゲームだし\nもう少し恋愛要素があるといいんだが……",
      "startTime": 205.166672643,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-mei017.m4a",
      "text": "恋愛要素……？\n芽衣が考えた恋愛観とは、違うのかな？",
      "startTime": 211.2333291371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな……アンケートに書いてくれた\n芽衣の「好き」はどんな「好き」なんだ？",
      "startTime": 219.3999958038,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-mei018.m4a",
      "text": "どんな……？　友達とか家族とか月ストのみんなとか\nドーナツとか猫ちゃんとか……？",
      "startTime": 228.7167122736,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "それだと、向こうが求めているものとは\n少し違うかもしれないな",
      "startTime": 235.1845679688,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-mei019.m4a",
      "text": "その好きって、芽衣の好きと同じじゃないの……？\n二つの好きがどう違うのか、分かんないよ……",
      "startTime": 242.1333291371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
